        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "In the midst of his despair, he approached Porthos, who blocked up the whole of the passage leading from the back shop to the shop itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
