        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "what an honor!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "The two others got under the counters, fearing Porthos might have a taste for human flesh.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"What cheese?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"The Dutch cheese, inside which a rat had made his way, and we found only the rind left.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "As soon as they had finished eating they set off.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000038_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000038_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "Porthos had all the taste and pride of a landed proprietor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"How so?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000063_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000063_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Good lad, good lad!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000063_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000063_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "How many acres of park have you got?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000064_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000064_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Of park?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000066_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000066_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Whereabouts, monsieur?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000066_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000066_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"At your chateau.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000068_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000068_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"What have you got, then?\" inquired Porthos, \"and why do you call it a country seat?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000071_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000071_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "I have rooms for a couple of friends, that's all.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000073_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000073_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"In the first place, they can walk about the king's forest, which is very beautiful.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000078_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000078_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Because I don't know where it ends; and, also, because it is full of poachers.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274115_000080_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274115/8063_274115_000080_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Because they hunt my game, and I hunt them-which, in these peaceful times, is for me a sufficiently pleasing picture of war on a small scale.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Oh! they shall have as much as they like.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "A few oats and a good bed-nothing more.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Some bran and water for my horse,\" said Porthos, \"for it is very warm, I think.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000009_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000009_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "The table was laid for two persons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"Life, monsieur,\" said Planchet, laughing, \"is capital which a man ought to invest as sensibly as he possibly can.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "Planchet turned to his housekeeper.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"You have before you,\" he said to her, \"the two gentlemen who influenced the greatest, gayest, grandest portion of my life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"I am from Antwerp,\" said the lady.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"You should not call her madame,\" said D'Artagnan.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "Porthos began to curl the other side of his mustache.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "\"The deuce,\" thought D'Artagnan, \"can Porthos have any intentions in that quarter?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "Porthos's heart began to expand as he said, \"I am hungry,\" and he sat himself beside Madame Truchen, whom he looked at in the most killing manner.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "While this was going on, the three men, Porthos especially, ate and drank gloriously,--it was wonderful to see them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8063/274116/8063_274116_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "The ten full bottles were ten empty ones by the time Truchen returned with the cheese.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8063_274116_000035_000002",
