        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "The two bearers of the corpse had unfastened the straps by which they carried the litter, and were letting their burden glide gently into the open grave.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
