        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "The cavalier kneels at the beginning, the young lady by and by gets tamed down, and then it is she who has to supplicate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
