        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8063",
        "content": "I ought to know that figure and peculiar style of walk.\" As he ran, the sound of his spurs and of his boots upon the hard ground of the street made a strange jingling noise; a fortunate circumstance in itself, which he was far from reckoning upon.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
